2026-05-27 11:29:33,640 [openai._base_client] DEBUG: Request options: {'method': 'post', 'url': '/chat/completions', 'headers': {'X-Stainless-Helper-Method': 'chat.completions.parse'}, 'files': None, 'idempotency_key': 'stainless-python-retry-2b336978-12d3-4a4f-b6cc-0fa2a5a1b190', 'post_parser': <function Completions.parse.<locals>.parser at 0x10a740510>, 'security': {'bearer_auth': True}, 'content': None, 'json_data': {'messages': [{'role': 'user', 'content': 'You are an accounts receivable specialist drafting a collections email on behalf of LedgerShield Inc.\n\nCLIENT DETAILS:\n  Client Name   : Cascade Partners\n  Amount Due    : $11,800.00 USD\n  Days Overdue  : 35 days\n  Contact Email : accounts@cascadepartners.com\n\nESCALATION TIER: LEGAL_NOTICE\nTONE INSTRUCTIONS: Use a strict, formal tone. Explicitly reference the contract enforcement clauses and state the specific consequences of continued non-payment, including suspension of services and potential legal action.\n\nPRIOR EMAIL HISTORY (oldest first):\n  Date: 2026-03-23\n  From: ar@ledgershield.com\n  To: accounts@cascadepartners.com\n  Subject: Invoice AR-1055 – $11,800.00 Due April 22, 2026 – LedgerShield Inc.\n  Body:\nHi Derek,\n\nHope you\'re having a good week. Please find Invoice AR-1055 attached for your records.\n\n  Invoice Number : AR-1055\n  Invoice Date   : March 23, 2026\n  Amount Due     : $11,800.00\n  Payment Due    : April 22, 2026\n  Payment Terms  : Net-30\n\nThis invoice reflects the Q1 2026 platform fee and the expanded data integration module activated for your team in February. Per your agreement, payment is due within 30 days of the invoice date.\n\nPlease confirm receipt at your earliest convenience, and let us know if you need any supporting documentation for your AP workflow.\n\nLooking forward to a smooth close on this one.\n\nWarm regards,\nSophia Reeves\nAccounts Receivable | LedgerShield Inc.\nar@ledgershield.com | +1 (415) 882-3300\n\n---\n\n  Date: 2026-05-13\n  From: accounts@cascadepartners.com\n  To: ar@ledgershield.com\n  Subject: Re: Invoice AR-1055 – $11,800.00 Due April 22, 2026 – LedgerShield Inc.\n  Body:\nHi Sophia,\n\nApologies for the delayed response – it\'s been a hectic couple of months on our end.\n\nWe\'re aware of the outstanding balance and we absolutely intend to take care of it. We\'ve been navigating some cash flow challenges following a slower-than-expected Q1 close. The team is working through it and we expect things to normalize soon.\n\nWe\'ll sort it out shortly – just bear with us a little longer. I\'ll be in touch once we have a clearer timeline.\n\nThanks for your patience.\n\nDerek Hollis\nAccounts | Cascade Partners\naccounts@cascadepartners.com\n\n---\n\n  Date: 2026-05-20\n  From: ar@ledgershield.com\n  To: accounts@cascadepartners.com\n  Subject: Re: Invoice AR-1055 – Payment Now 28 Days Past Due – Action Required\n  Body:\nHi Derek,\n\nThank you for your note last week. We understand that cash flow pressures arise, and we appreciate you reaching out.\n\nHowever, Invoice AR-1055 for $11,800.00 is now 28 days past its due date of April 22, 2026, and we haven\'t received a payment commitment with a specific date.\n\nWe\'d like to work with you on a resolution. Options we can accommodate:\n  1. Full payment at your earliest convenience\n  2. A structured payment plan (e.g., two installments over 30 days) with a written schedule\n\nCould you please reply with a specific payment date or propose a plan by this Friday, May 22? Without a confirmed timeline, we will need to escalate this account in accordance with our collections process.\n\nWe value the relationship with Cascade Partners and want to resolve this collaboratively. Please don\'t hesitate to call me directly at +1 (415) 882-3300 if it\'s easier to discuss.\n\nBest,\nSophia Reeves\nAccounts Receivable | LedgerShield Inc.\nar@ledgershield.com | +1 (415) 882-3300\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\nDraft a collections email appropriate for the escalation tier. The email must:\n1. Open with a clear, direct reference to the outstanding invoice and amount.\n2. Reference prior communications where relevant.\n3. State a specific payment deadline (within 7 days).\n4. Apply the tone described above without deviation.\n5. Include a professional sign-off from the LedgerShield AR team.\n\nFill all fields of the CollectionsEmail model:\n  - recipient: the client\'s billing contact email (accounts@cascadepartners.com)\n  - client_name: exactly "Cascade Partners"\n  - subject: a concise subject line referencing the overdue balance\n  - body: the complete email body text\n  - escalation_tier: exactly "legal_notice"\n'}], 'model': 'gpt-4o-mini', 'response_format': {'type': 'json_schema', 'json_schema': {'schema': {'properties': {'recipient': {'title': 'Recipient', 'type': 'string'}, 'client_name': {'title': 'Client Name', 'type': 'string'}, 'subject': {'title': 'Subject', 'type': 'string'}, 'body': {'title': 'Body', 'type': 'string'}, 'escalation_tier': {'enum': ['firm_reminder', 'legal_notice', 'final_demand'], 'title': 'Escalation Tier', 'type': 'string'}}, 'required': ['recipient', 'client_name', 'subject', 'body', 'escalation_tier'], 'title': 'CollectionsEmail', 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'name': 'CollectionsEmail', 'strict': True}}, 'stream': False}}
