--------------------------------------------------\nPAYMENT INSTRUCTIONS\n\nPlease remit payment within 30 days of the invoice date.\n\nWire Transfer:\n  Bank Name    : First National Commercial Bank\n  Account Name : Acme Corp Operating Account\n  Routing No.  : 021000021\n  Account No.  : 7840239105\n\nACH / Check:\n  Payable to: Acme Corp\n  Mail to: Acme Corp, Attn: Accounts Receivable\n           4800 Technology Drive, Suite 200\n           Austin, TX 78701\n\nOnline Payment Portal: https://pay.acmecorp.com (Invoice # required)\n\nPlease reference invoice number INV-2024-0847 on all payments.\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nBILLING CONTACT\n\nQuestions regarding this invoice should be directed to:\n\n  Acme Corp Billing Team\n  billing@acmecorp.com\n  +1 (512) 944-2200 ext. 5\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nThank you for your business. We appreciate your continued partnership.\n================================================================================\n\n'}], 'model': 'gpt-4o-mini', 'response_format': {'type': 'json_schema', 'json_schema': {'schema': {'$defs': {'LineItem': {'properties': {'description': {'title': 'Description', 'type': 'string'}, 'quantity': {'title': 'Quantity', 'type': 'number'}, 'unit_price': {'title': 'Unit Price', 'type': 'number'}, 'line_total': {'title': 'Line Total', 'type': 'number'}}, 'required': ['description', 'quantity', 'unit_price', 'line_total'], 'title': 'LineItem', 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}}, 'properties': {'vendor_name': {'title': 'Vendor Name', 'type': 'string'}, 'invoice_number': {'title': 'Invoice Number', 'type': 'string'}, 'invoice_date': {'title': 'Invoice Date', 'type': 'string'}, 'due_date': {'title': 'Due Date', 'type': 'string'}, 'line_items': {'items': {'$ref': '#/$defs/LineItem'}, 'title': 'Line Items', 'type': 'array'}, 'subtotal': {'title': 'Subtotal', 'type': 'number'}, 'tax': {